'From Squeak 2.3 of January 14, 1999 on 3 February 1999 at 10:31:03 am'!"Change Set:		VarNodeTypeDate:			3 February 1999Author:			Leandro CanigliaDefines 'type' for VariableNodes to facilitate access for, eg, type inference."!!VariableNode methodsFor: 'testing' stamp: 'di 2/3/1999 09:41'!type	"This code attempts to reconstruct the type from its encoding in code.		This allows one to test, for instance, (aNode type = LdInstType)."	| type |	code < 0 ifTrue: [^ code negated].	code < 256 ifFalse: [^ code // 256].	type _ CodeBases findFirst: [:one | code < one].	type = 0		ifTrue: [^ 5]		ifFalse: [^ type - 1]! !